description: Sturdy Good Looks - Grab Hold of your Style - Take control of your image with this eye-catching case. The raised hexagonal pattern accentuates the case’s layers while creating a surface that is easy to grip. Max Grip, Max Protection The thin, yet durable material is a stylish way to keep your iPod's surface free of scratches and scuffs, without adding extra bulk.
title: Belkin Max Case for Apple iPod touch 4G-Fountain Blue/Yellow Cab
